<dl>
<div class=".faqAccordion .faqAccordion2">
    <dt class="acc_trigger specic_tab"><a href="#toggle1">Is electric kettle good for health?</a></dt>
    <dd class="acc_container specic_tab">
        <div class="block">Drinking hot water has additional health benefits. Electric kettles heat, boil water within a short time. Wonderchef electric kettles are good for health. The kettles are made of high grade stainless steel or borosilicate glass which is food grade, anti-rust and does not affect the taste or quality of water. The heating coil is covered and does not come in contact with heating water inside the kettle making Wonderchef kettles your healthy choice.
       </div>
    </dd>
    
    <dt class="acc_trigger specic_tab"><a href="#toggle2">Are electric kettles safe to use?</a></dt>
    <dd class="acc_container">
        <div class="block">Yes, Wonderchef electric kettles are safe to use. The heating coil is covered and does not come in contact with water inside the kettle. Wonderchef electric kettles have an inbuilt thermostat, the kettle will auto-shut down when the temperature inside reaches boiling point. The drip-free spout and lid lock give additional safety to prevent hot water from spilling out. Kettle handle is heat resistant for easy handling. In double walled Wonderchef kettles like Luxe Ivory, Crimson Edge, Multi-cook Kettles the outer plastic body is cool touch.
      </div>
    </dd>
    
    <dt class="acc_trigger specic_tab"><a href="#toggle3">What is better, plastic or steel body kettle? </a></dt>
    <dd class="acc_container">
        <div class="block">Steel Kettles – In Wonderchef steel kettles Crescent/ Cool-Touch/ Prato electric/Crimson edge /Luxe Multi-cook, the steel body is better choice than plastic for electric kettles. Stainless Steel is not affected by heat. Wonderchef electric kettle made of high grade Stainless steel which is food grade, does not rust, and does not affect the taste of water.
Wonderchef Azure electric kettle is made of Borosilicate glass body is better choice than plastic for electric kettles. Glass can withstand high temperature. Azure glass kettle material is free of toxins and does not affect the taste of water when it comes in contact.

      </div>
    </dd>
   <dt class="acc_trigger specic_tab"><a href="#toggle4">What is the use of electric kettle?</a></dt>
    <dd class="acc_container">
        <div class="block">An electric kettle is used to boiling/heating water. This hot water can be utilized to make tea, coffee, soups and more.
      </div>
    </dd>
